    • Method Detail

      • getConceptDetails

        ISnomedBrowserConcept getConceptDetails(IComponentRef conceptRef,
                                        List<ExtendedLocale> extendedLocales)
        Retrieves information strongly connected to a concept in a single request.
        Parameters:
        conceptRef - the component reference pointing to the concept to retrieve (may not be null)
        extendedLocales - the ExtendedLocales to inspect when determining FSN and preferred synonym, in decreasing order of preference
        Returns:
        the aggregated content for the requested concept
        Throws:
        CodeSystemNotFoundException - if a code system with the given short name is not registered
        CodeSystemVersionNotFoundException - if a code system version for the code system with the given identifier is not registered
        ComponentNotFoundException - if the component identifier does not match any concept on the given task

      • getConceptParents

        List<ISnomedBrowserParentConcept> getConceptParents(IComponentRef conceptRef,
                                                    List<ExtendedLocale> extendedLocales)
        Retrieves a list of parent concepts for a single identifier.
        Parameters:
        conceptRef - the component reference pointing to the concept whose parents should be retrieved (may not be null)
        extendedLocales - the ExtendedLocales to inspect when determining FSN, in decreasing order of preference
        Returns:
        the parent concept list for the requested concept
        Throws:
        CodeSystemNotFoundException - if a code system with the given short name is not registered
        CodeSystemVersionNotFoundException - if a code system version for the code system with the given identifier is not registered
        ComponentNotFoundException - if the component identifier does not match any concept on the given task

      • getConceptChildren

        List<ISnomedBrowserChildConcept> getConceptChildren(IComponentRef conceptRef,
                                                    List<ExtendedLocale> extendedLocales,
                                                    boolean stated)
        Retrieves a list of child concepts for a single identifier.
        Parameters:
        conceptRef - the component reference pointing to the concept whose children should be retrieved (may not be null)
        extendedLocales - the ExtendedLocales to inspect when determining FSN, in decreasing order of preference
        stated - true if stated children should be returned, false if inferred
        Returns:
        the child concept list for the requested concept
        Throws:
        CodeSystemNotFoundException - if a code system with the given short name is not registered
        CodeSystemVersionNotFoundException - if a code system version for the code system with the given identifier is not registered
        ComponentNotFoundException - if the component identifier does not match any concept on the given task

      • getDescriptions

        List<ISnomedBrowserDescriptionResult> getDescriptions(IStorageRef storageRef,
                                                      String query,
                                                      List<ExtendedLocale> extendedLocales,
                                                      ISnomedBrowserDescriptionResult.TermType resultConceptTermType,
                                                      int offset,
                                                      int limit)
        Retrieves a list of descriptions matching the entered query string.
        Parameters:
        storageRef - the storage reference locating the version and branch to search on (may not be null)
        query - the query text (must be at least 3 characters long)
        extendedLocales - the ExtendedLocales to inspect when determining FSN, in decreasing order of preference
        offset - the offset in the result set (may not be negative)
        limit - the maximal number of results to return
        Returns:
        the search result list of descriptions
        Throws:
        CodeSystemNotFoundException - if a code system with the given short name is not registered
        CodeSystemVersionNotFoundException - if a code system version for the code system with the given identifier is not registered
        IllegalArgumentException - if the query is null or too short

      • getConstants

        Map<String,ISnomedBrowserConstant> getConstants(String branch,
                                                List<ExtendedLocale> extendedLocales)
        Retrieves a map of enum constants and corresponding concepts.
        Parameters:
        storageRef - the storage reference locating the version and branch to inspect (may not be null)
        extendedLocales - the ExtendedLocales to inspect when determining FSN, in decreasing order of preference
        Returns:
        a map with keys as constant identifiers, and values as corresponding concept ID-FSN pairs
        Throws:
        CodeSystemNotFoundException - if a code system with the given short name is not registered
        CodeSystemVersionNotFoundException - if a code system version for the code system with the given identifier is not registered
